{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-work-template-js","path":"/audiovamp/","result":{"data":{"page":{"id":"95220a6a-9ad3-5935-ac7e-7453a52535ab","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3b0376cb1ed37ea4d117b704b09a3e22/d1f95/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 77%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/3b0376cb1ed37ea4d117b704b09a3e22/d1f95/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3b0376cb1ed37ea4d117b704b09a3e22/d1f95/1.jpg 500w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>I built an audio player using the <a href=\"https://www.fmod.com/\">FMOD</a> library, <a href=\"https://www.qt.io/\">QT</a> and C++.</p>\n<p>It supports WAV, MP3, OGG, XM, S3M and other audio formats. I also created an oscilloscope visualisation, an spectrum analyser, time line, volume control, balance, loading files from a URL and a playlist feature.</p>","fields":{"prefix":"2004"},"frontmatter":{"title":"AudioVamp","categories":"desktop design ux prototype","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/3b0376cb1ed37ea4d117b704b09a3e22/47498/1.jpg"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/audiovamp/","source":"work"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}